Interface FragmentChangeListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DeploymentActivity, GridSetupActivity

    public interface FragmentChangeListener
    This Interface provides Activities and Fragments with a method to replace the currently running fragment with another Fragment.
    See Also:
    Fragment, Activity
